quota:

quotacheck -cugv <location>
2 new files are created that are .grp and .usr

then use:
quotaon --help
quotaon -ap
then we do edquota to edit quota

to get report status for quota: repquota

LVM:
must have the lvm2 pkg or do yum install lvm2
pvdisplay = physical volume display
pvcreate = creates primary vol to physical

vgdisplay = volume group display
vgcreate = create vg

xfs_growfs = for 
